              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "> The transcript begins by explaining how the transcription process will be carried out using AI technology. Any parts that the AI cannot understand will be reviewed and filled in by a human. The finalized transcript will be sent to the interviewee for review, allowing for any corrections or clarifications before being finalized."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "** transcription, AI, review process, human intervention, corrections **"
