              {
                "text": "> The interviewee is informed that with their permission, the finalized transcript will be archived in the digital archives of Connecticut, maintained by UConn. This archive serves as a permanent repository, ensuring that historical and personal data, such as the interviewee's experiences starting out, are preserved."
